Schedule Task & Poll SCM

Scheduled Project
1.	Click on any project
2.	Configure 
3.	Build triggers
4.	Build Periodically
5.	* * * * * 
6.	Save
7.	You can see automatic build after every minute
8.	You can manually trigger build as well
Source Code Polling
1.	Now go to Jenkins Homepage
2.	Go to MyMavenProject 
3.	Configure
4.	Now go to Build trigger
5.	Check Poll SCM option
6.	Schedule 
7.	* * * * * 
8.	 Save
9.	Now go to GitHub account
10.	Do some changes in README.md
11.	Commit changes
12.	You can see after 1 min, it builds automatically
